 href=\"/en/global/about/governance\" target=\"_self\">Governance</a></li>\r\n                                                        <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/talent\" target=\"_self\">Human Capital</a></li>\r\n                                        </ul>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </li>\r\n                    <li>\r\n                        <span>\r\n                            Our Business\r\n                            <button type=\"button\" class=\"u-pc-none\"></button>\r\n                        </span>\r\n                        <div class=\"l-mnavi\">\r\n                            <div class=\"c-inr\">\r\n                                <p class=\"l-mnavi__ttl u-sp-none\">Our Business</p>\r\n                                    <div class=\"l-mnavi__menu\">\r\n                                        <ul>\r\n                                                        <li><a href=\"/en/global/business\" target=\"_self\">Business Fields</a></li>\r\n                                        </ul>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <ul class=\"l-gnavi__lang u-sp\">\r\n        <li><a href=\"/ja/global/about/message\">日本語</a></li>\n<li class=\"is-current\"><a href=\"/en/global/about/message\">英語</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zhcn/global/about/message\">中文（简体字）</a></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</nav>\r\n<div class=\"l-header__search u-sp-none\">\r\n    <button type=\"button\"></button>\r\n    <div class=\"l-header__search__form c-wrap\">\r\n        <div class=\"c-inr\">\r\n            <form name=\"SS_searchForm\" id=\"ss-form1\" action=\"/en/global/search\" method=\"get\">\n    <button class=\"siteSearch-button\" type=\"submit\"></button>\n    <input class=\"siteSearch-input\" id=\"ss-query1\" type=\"text\" name=\"query\" placeholder=\"Please enter keywords\" />\n</form>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n    </header>\r\n    <main class=\"l-main theme-single theme-second theme-GHQ\">\r\n    <article class=\"l-article\">\r\n        \r\n    <div class=\"fxb-section\">\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-container-fruid\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-col-md-12\">\r\n                    <div class=\"mainVisual mainVisual-basic\">\r\n                        <div class=\"_cover\">\r\n                            <div class=\"_trim\"><img src=\"/global/-/media/Images/global/VisualCarousel/mv_item02_pc.jpg?h=550&amp;iar=0&amp;w=1400\" class=\"fit-image\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"550\" /></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"_content\">\r\n                            <div class=\"_catch\">\r\n                                <h1 class=\"_largeTitle\"><span class=\"visible-mobile\">Message from<br>the President and CEO</span></h1>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"fxb-section bg-blueLighter border-top-grayLight\" id=\"breadcrumb\">\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-container\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-col-md-12\">\r\n                    <div class=\"breadcrumbs\">\r\n                        <ol>\r\n\r\n                            <li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                    <a itemprop=\"item\" href=\"/en/global/\">\r\n                                            <span itemprop=\"name\">Home</span>\r\n                                    </a>\r\n                                <meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"1\">\r\n                            </li>\r\n                            <li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                        <span itemprop=\"name\">About Us</span>\r\n                                <meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"2\">\r\n                            </li>\r\n                            <li itemprop=\"itemListElement\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/ListItem\">\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                        <span itemprop=\"name\">Message from the President and CEO</span>\r\n                                <meta itemprop=\"position\" content=\"3\">\r\n                            </li>\r\n                        </ol>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-section  bg-md-transparent \" id=\"\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-container-fluid\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n<section class=\"layer-title\">\n  <h2 class=\"_largeTitle\">Message from<br>the President and CEO</h2>\n</section>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-section  \" id=\"\">\r\n            <div class=\"fxb-container\">\r\n                <div class=\"fxb-row\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"fxb-col-md-12\" >\r\n                        <p class=\"mt-larger-contain\">The business environment surrounding us continues to evolve at an unprecedented pace, driven by rising geopolitical risks, shifts in supply chains, and the rapid advancement of AI, among other factors, further heightening uncertainty.</p>\n\n<p>To respond to these challenges, the Sumitomo Corporation Group is leveraging the knowledge, networks, and business development capabilities it has cultivated across diverse regions and business domains. At the same time, we are strengthening businesses where we have competitive advantages while enhancing our resilience and agility to adapt to changes in the business environment.</p>\n<p>In FY2025, we achieved a record-high consolidated net income of 600.3 billion yen. This achievement reflects the steady progress of the initiatives we have put into action under our Medium-Term Management Plan 2026, as well as the trust and support of our stakeholders, including shareholders and investors, business partners, local communities, and our employees.</p>\n<p><a class=\"link-angle-arrow-right\" href=\"/en/global/about/principles/mid-term\">The Medium-Term Management Plan 2026</a> &nbsp; has now entered its final year. Through this plan, we aim to become &ldquo;No.1 in Each Field&rdquo; by sharpening our competitive advantages and achieving growth through addressing social challenges. To realize this, we will further reinforce our strengths, while steadily advancing asset replacement and business turnaround initiatives, thereby continuing to enhance the quality of our business portfolio.</p>\n<p>We also recognize the evolution of digital and AI technologies as a significant growth opportunity. Accordingly, we have formulated our Digital & AI Strategy (DAIS) to drive business transformation across the Group. By combining the expertise cultivated across our businesses with digital solutions, and leveraging flexible thinking and strong execution, we will contribute to the transformation of society and industries.</p>\n<p>Guided by the Sumitomo Business Philosophy and the Management Principles of the Sumitomo Corporation Group, we are committed to our corporate message: <a class=\"link-angle-arrow-right\" href=\"/en/global/about/corporate-message\"> &ldquo;Enriching lives and the world&rdquo;</a>. By deepening the trust we share with our stakeholders, we will continue to address social challenges through our business activities and achieve sustainable growth.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mb-medium-contain\">We sincerely appreciate your continued support for the Sumitomo Corporation Group.</p>\n\n<div class=\"signatureArea\">\n<p class=\"text-weight-bold\">Shingo Ueno<br>\nPresident and Chief Executive Officer</p>\n</div>\r\n                        \r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class=\"l-lnavi c-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"c-inr\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"l-lnavi__ttl u-f--dmst\">About Us</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"l-lnavi__menu\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n        <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/corporate-message\">Corporate Message</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/principles\">Principles and Strategy (Medium-Term Management Plan)</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/message\">Message from the President and CEO</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/profile\">Corporate Profile</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/at-a-glance\">At a Glance</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/history\">History</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/network\">Global Network</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/governance\">Governance</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"/en/global/about/talent\">Human Capital</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</section><div class=\"l-sns c-wrap\">\r\n    <div class=\"c-inr\">\r\n            <h3 class=\"u-f--dmst-sns u-tac text-align-center\">\r\n                Social Media <br class=\"u-sp\" />\r\nOfficial Account\r\n            </h3>\r\n                    <ul class=\"l-sns__btn\">\r\n                <style>\n  .l-sns__btn, .l-sns__share {\n  padding-left: 0;\n  }\n  .l-sns__btn li {\n    width: 215px;\n  }\n  @media screen and (min-width: 1px) and (max-width: 768px) {\n    .l-sns__btn li {\n      width: 172px;\n    }\n  }\n  @media screen and (min-width: 1px) and (max-width: 460px) {\n    .l-sns__btn li {\n      widt